From d3b013aabc47fa610d57cd35653e9e26fbdf2490 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tim Pietrusky <tim.pietrusky@runpod.io>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 10:53:40 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 08/19] =?UTF-8?q?turboquant(cuda):=20fix=20BSNH/BNSH=20str?=
 =?UTF-8?q?ide=20mismatch=20in=20encode=20kernel=20=E2=80=94=20quality=200?=
