From 363b6dfa88f856e92778e567d3f4a9b6ccf74313 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tim Pietrusky <tim.pietrusky@runpod.io>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 12:19:32 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 10/19] =?UTF-8?q?turboquant:=20option=20A=20=E2=80=94=20ru?=
