From b61ef5234f3622f692fe671098a0db360871f1bc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tim Pietrusky <tim.pietrusky@runpod.io>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 13:26:26 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 12/19] =?UTF-8?q?turboquant(cuda):=20v7=20=E2=80=94=20skip?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20lossy=20round-trip=20for=20new=20tokens=20+=20causal=20early?=
